{"type": "bundle", "id": "bundle--c3ef6a20-1f12-5d20-b26d-3eb3330fad1e", "objects": [{"type": "identity", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "created": "2026-04-03T02:29:44Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T02:29:44Z", "name": "VigilIntel", "identity_class": "organization"}, {"type": "marking-definition", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "definition_type": "tlp", "definition": {"tlp": "clear"}}, {"type": "extension-definition", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "extension-definition--f8d78575-edfd-406e-8e84-6162a8450f5b", "name": "PAP", "description": "This defines PAP as a STIX extension", "created": "2022-10-01T00:00:00.000Z", "modified": "2022-10-01T00:00:00.000Z", "schema": "https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/tree/master/extension-definition-specifications/pap", "version": "1.0.0", "extension_types": ["property-extension"]}, {"type": "marking-definition", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92", "created": "2022-10-01T00:00:00.000Z", "name": "PAP:CLEAR", "extensions": {"extension-definition--f8d78575-edfd-406e-8e84-6162a8450f5b": {"extension_type": "property-extension", "pap": "clear"}}}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "note--e229fa1a-dddc-5906-93ca-5968ad53700a", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "content": "## Summary\n**FR:** Le paysage de la menace au 3 avril 2026 est domin\u00e9 par des compromissions de la cha\u00eene d'approvisionnement \u00e0 fort impact (Axios), l'industrialisation des techniques de neutralisation des EDR (Qilin) et une recrudescence des exploits mobiles \u00e9tatiques (Coldriver). Les tensions g\u00e9opolitiques au Moyen-Orient et en Ukraine continuent de se manifester par des attaques destructrices (wipers) et des op\u00e9rations d'influence coordonn\u00e9es. Par ailleurs, l'infiltration syst\u00e9matique des d\u00e9partements IT occidentaux par des agents nord-cor\u00e9ens (NKITW) repr\u00e9sente un risque croissant pour l'int\u00e9grit\u00e9 des entreprises. En France, l'augmentation significative de l'activit\u00e9 des botnets Mirai souligne la vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9 persistante des infrastructures IoT.\n\n**EN:** The threat landscape on April 3rd, 2026, is dominated by high-impact supply chain compromises (Axios), the industrialization of EDR-blinding techniques (Qilin), and a surge in state-sponsored mobile exploits (Coldriver). Geopolitical tensions in the Middle East and Ukraine continue to manifest through destructive wiper attacks and coordinated influence operations. Furthermore, the systematic infiltration of Western IT departments by North Korean agents (NKITW) represents a growing long-term risk to corporate integrity. In France, the significant increase in Mirai-driven botnet activity highlights the persistent vulnerability of IoT infrastructures.\n", "object_refs": ["identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea"], "abstract": "Strategic | Daily brief (2026-04-03)", "labels": ["strategic", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--eb5dff66-0d13-5117-be00-1829e1f10d6b", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "related-to", "source_ref": "note--e229fa1a-dddc-5906-93ca-5968ad53700a", "target_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "description": "Strategic note linked to referenced object", "labels": ["strategic", "note-link", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "note--d18872ab-07e8-539f-93de-b4b75f8f5240", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "content": "## Summary\n**FR:** Frappes de drones ukrainiens sur les ports p\u00e9troliers russes (Ust-Luga, Primorsk) suivies de narratifs du Kremlin accusant l'Occident de pr\u00e9parer des coups d'\u00c9tat dans des nations alli\u00e9es comme la Hongrie.\n\n**EN:** Ukrainian drone strikes on Russian oil ports (Ust-Luga, Primorsk) followed by Kremlin narratives accusing the West of preparing coups in allied nations like Hungary.\n\n## Context\n- Date: 2026-04-03\n- Sector: ['D\u00e9fense', '\u00c9nergie'] / ['Defense', 'Energy']\n- Theme: Escalade du conflit Ukraine-Russie / Ukraine-Russia Conflict Escalation\n\n## Tags\ngeopolitics, energy, conflict\n\n## Sources\n- EUvsDisinfo\n", "object_refs": ["identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea"], "abstract": "Geopolitical | Escalade du conflit Ukraine-Russie (2026-04-03)", "external_references": [{"source_name": "source", "url": "EUvsDisinfo"}], "labels": ["geopolitics", "energy", "conflict", "geopolitical", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--98328220-ccc7-53a2-8e93-76693e54307f", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "related-to", "source_ref": "note--d18872ab-07e8-539f-93de-b4b75f8f5240", "target_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "description": "Geopolitical note linked to referenced object", "labels": ["geopolitics", "energy", "conflict", "geopolitical", "note-link", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "note--f0c2cf26-2cff-5838-8154-640c1fdfba79", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "content": "## Summary\n**FR:** L'IRGC a d\u00e9sign\u00e9 18 entreprises technologiques am\u00e9ricaines comme cibles l\u00e9gitimes. Parall\u00e8lement, les Houthis, le Hezbollah et l'Iran coordonnent des menaces cyber et physiques dans la r\u00e9gion de la mer Rouge.\n\n**EN:** The IRGC has designated 18 US tech companies as legitimate targets. Concurrently, Houthis, Hezbollah, and Iran are coordinating cyber and physical threats in the Red Sea region.\n\n## Context\n- Date: 2026-04-03\n- Sector: ['Technologie', 'D\u00e9fense'] / ['Technology', 'Defense']\n- Theme: Tensions Cyber au Moyen-Orient / Middle East Cyber Tensions\n\n## Tags\nirgc, middle east, threat\n\n## Sources\n- Flare\n", "object_refs": ["identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea"], "abstract": "Geopolitical | Tensions Cyber au Moyen-Orient (2026-04-03)", "external_references": [{"source_name": "source", "url": "Flare"}], "labels": ["irgc", "middle east", "threat", "geopolitical", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--a73c01b5-5556-549a-97f9-e20bb9129411", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "related-to", "source_ref": "note--f0c2cf26-2cff-5838-8154-640c1fdfba79", "target_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "description": "Geopolitical note linked to referenced object", "labels": ["irgc", "middle east", "threat", "geopolitical", "note-link", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "threat-actor", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "threat-actor--69a9a08c-4ac1-5f3c-839d-76dd91611e06", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "name": "Handala Hack", "threat_actor_types": ["unknown"], "labels": ["threat-actor", "wiper", "medical", "intune", "breach", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "identity", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "identity--ed9f32dd-46b4-576a-9f0e-27737fd225e0", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "name": "Stryker", "identity_class": "organization", "labels": ["victim", "wiper", "medical", "intune", "breach", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--399263bc-cc7a-52ba-80c2-dfce1d0a7a85", "created": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-04-03T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "targets", "source_ref": "threat-actor--69a9a08c-4ac1-5f3c-839d-76dd91611e06", "target_ref": "identity--ed9f32dd-46b4-576a-9f0e-27737fd225e0", "labels": ["breach", "wiper", "medical", "intune", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "note--733ce550